              <p class="mt-4">‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û...</p>
            </div>
            <img id="modal-image" class="max-w-full max-h-[60vh] object-contain hidden" src="" alt="‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏Ç‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏¢" 
